{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":312,"text":"How many of you have been to Oklahoma City?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":2485,"text":"Raise your hand. Yeah?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":3775,"text":"How many of you have not been to Oklahoma City"},{"time":5924,"text":"and have no idea who I am? (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9933,"text":"Most of you. Let me give you\na little bit of background."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12731,"text":"Oklahoma City started in the most"},{"time":15173,"text":"unique way imaginable."},{"time":16941,"text":"Back on a spring day in 1889,"},{"time":19763,"text":"the federal government held what they called"},{"time":21350,"text":"a land run."},{"time":23109,"text":"They literally lined up the settlers"},{"time":24803,"text":"along an imaginary line,"},{"time":26426,"text":"and they fired off a gun,"},{"time":27851,"text":"and the settlers roared across the countryside"},{"time":29636,"text":"and put down a stake,"},{"time":31752,"text":"and wherever they put down that stake,"},{"time":33288,"text":"that was their new home."},{"time":34996,"text":"And at the end of the very first day,"},{"time":37366,"text":"the population of Oklahoma City"},{"time":39116,"text":"had gone from zero to 10,000,"},{"time":43022,"text":"and our planning department"},{"time":44363,"text":"is still paying for that."},{"time":48283,"text":"The citizens got together on that first day"},{"time":50780,"text":"and elected a mayor."},{"time":53032,"text":"And then they shot him."},{"time":54839,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":59947,"text":"That's not really all that funny"},{"time":62430,"text":"-- (Laughter) --"},{"time":63934,"text":"but it allows me to see what type of audience"},{"time":65854,"text":"I'm dealing with, so I appreciate the feedback."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70216,"text":"The 20th century was fairly kind to Oklahoma City."},{"time":72993,"text":"Our economy was based on commodities,"},{"time":75454,"text":"so the price of cotton or the price of wheat,"},{"time":78253,"text":"and ultimately the price of oil and natural gas."},{"time":81566,"text":"And along the way, we became a city"},{"time":83678,"text":"of innovation."},{"time":85724,"text":"The shopping cart was invented in Oklahoma City."},{"time":89597,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":94737,"text":"The parking meter, invented in Oklahoma City."},{"time":100037,"text":"You're welcome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103783,"text":"Having an economy, though,"},{"time":105479,"text":"that relates to commodities\ncan give you some ups and some downs,"},{"time":108626,"text":"and that was certainly the case\nin Oklahoma City's history."},{"time":111223,"text":"In the 1970s, when it appeared"},{"time":113580,"text":"that the price of energy would never retreat,"},{"time":115403,"text":"our economy was soaring,"},{"time":117137,"text":"and then in the early 1980s, it cratered quickly."},{"time":120719,"text":"The price of energy dropped."},{"time":123190,"text":"Our banks began to fail."},{"time":124942,"text":"Before the end of the decade,"},{"time":126500,"text":"100 banks had failed in the state of Oklahoma."},{"time":130387,"text":"There was no bailout on the horizon."},{"time":132938,"text":"Our banking industry, our oil and gas industry,"},{"time":135243,"text":"our commercial real estate industry,"},{"time":137279,"text":"were all at the bottom of the economic scale."},{"time":140482,"text":"Young people were leaving Oklahoma City in droves"},{"time":143127,"text":"for Washington and Dallas and Houston\nand New York and Tokyo,"},{"time":146042,"text":"anywhere where they could \nfind a job that measured up"},{"time":148149,"text":"to their educational attainment,"},{"time":149820,"text":"because in Oklahoma City,\nthe good jobs just weren't there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153051,"text":"But along at the end of the '80s"},{"time":154767,"text":"came an enterprising businessman"},{"time":157595,"text":"who became mayor named Ron Norick."},{"time":159604,"text":"Ron Norick eventually figured out"},{"time":161351,"text":"that the secret to economic development"},{"time":163288,"text":"wasn't incentivizing companies up front,"},{"time":165449,"text":"it was about creating a place\nwhere businesses wanted to locate,"},{"time":168503,"text":"and so he pushed an initiative called MAPS"},{"time":171515,"text":"that basically was a penny-on-the-dollar sales tax"},{"time":173920,"text":"to build a bunch of stuff."},{"time":176232,"text":"It built a new sports arena,"},{"time":178207,"text":"a new canal downtown,"},{"time":180386,"text":"it fixed up our performing arts center,"},{"time":182747,"text":"a new baseball stadium downtown,"},{"time":185414,"text":"a lot of things to improve the quality of life."},{"time":187258,"text":"And the economy indeed seemed to start"},{"time":189671,"text":"showing some signs of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191703,"text":"The next mayor came along."},{"time":194061,"text":"He started MAPS for Kids,"},{"time":195838,"text":"rebuilt the entire inner city school system,"},{"time":198565,"text":"all 75 buildings either built anew or refurbished."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203319,"text":"And then, in 2004,"},{"time":206540,"text":"in this rare collective lack of judgment"},{"time":211244,"text":"bordering on civil disobedience,"},{"time":213872,"text":"the citizens elected me mayor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217840,"text":"Now the city I inherited"},{"time":220044,"text":"was just on the verge"},{"time":221888,"text":"of coming out of its slumbering economy,"},{"time":225289,"text":"and for the very first time,"},{"time":226980,"text":"we started showing up on the lists."},{"time":230119,"text":"Now you know the lists I'm talking about."},{"time":232136,"text":"The media and the Internet"},{"time":233919,"text":"love to rank cities."},{"time":236465,"text":"And in Oklahoma City,"},{"time":238540,"text":"we'd never really been on lists before."},{"time":241221,"text":"So I thought it was kind of cool"},{"time":242927,"text":"when they came out with these\npositive lists and we were on there."},{"time":245623,"text":"We weren't anywhere close to the top,"},{"time":247321,"text":"but we were on the list, we were somebody."},{"time":250818,"text":"Best city to get a job,"},{"time":252648,"text":"best city to start a business,"},{"time":254663,"text":"best downtown --"},{"time":256456,"text":"Oklahoma City."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258930,"text":"And then came the list"},{"time":262235,"text":"of the most obese cities in the country."},{"time":267781,"text":"And there we were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270884,"text":"Now I like to point out that we were on that list"},{"time":273028,"text":"with a lot of really cool places."},{"time":275526,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":276749,"text":"Dallas and Houston and New Orleans"},{"time":280005,"text":"and Atlanta and Miami."},{"time":281715,"text":"You know, these are cities that, typically,"},{"time":283212,"text":"you're not embarrassed to be associated with."},{"time":285860,"text":"But nonetheless, I didn't like being on the list."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290128,"text":"And about that time, I got on the scales."},{"time":294473,"text":"And I weighed 220 pounds."},{"time":296599,"text":"And then I went to this website"},{"time":298102,"text":"sponsored by the federal government,"},{"time":299952,"text":"and I typed in my height, I typed in my weight,"},{"time":303625,"text":"and I pushed Enter,"},{"time":304954,"text":"and it came back and said \"obese.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":309004,"text":"I thought, \"What a stupid website.\""},{"time":311257,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":314132,"text":"\"I'm not obese. I would know if I was obese.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":320377,"text":"And then I started getting honest with myself"},{"time":322868,"text":"about what had become\nmy lifelong struggle with obesity,"},{"time":327794,"text":"and I noticed this pattern,"},{"time":329674,"text":"that I was gaining about two or three pounds a year,"},{"time":332365,"text":"and then about every 10 years,\nI'd drop 20 or 30 pounds."},{"time":335671,"text":"And then I'd do it again."},{"time":337233,"text":"And I had this huge closet full of clothes,"},{"time":339566,"text":"and I could only wear a third of it at any one time,"},{"time":342933,"text":"and only I knew which part of the closet I could wear."},{"time":347045,"text":"But it all seemed fairly normal, going through it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352595,"text":"Well, I finally decided I needed to lose weight,"},{"time":355677,"text":"and I knew I could because\nI'd done it so many times before,"},{"time":358094,"text":"so I simply stopped eating as much."},{"time":360332,"text":"I had always exercised."},{"time":361587,"text":"That really wasn't the part of the equation"},{"time":363462,"text":"that I needed to work on."},{"time":365375,"text":"But I had been eating 3,000 calories a day,"},{"time":368204,"text":"and I cut it to 2,000 calories a day,"},{"time":370486,"text":"and the weight came off. I lost about a pound a week"},{"time":373377,"text":"for about 40 weeks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377283,"text":"Along the way, though,"},{"time":378828,"text":"I started examining my city,"},{"time":382848,"text":"its culture, its infrastructure,"},{"time":386344,"text":"trying to figure out why our specific city"},{"time":389236,"text":"seemed to have a problem with obesity."},{"time":393635,"text":"And I came to the conclusion"},{"time":395811,"text":"that we had built an incredible quality of life"},{"time":399669,"text":"if you happen to be a car."},{"time":403089,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":406324,"text":"But if you happen to be a person,"},{"time":409864,"text":"you are combatting the car seemingly at every turn."},{"time":414433,"text":"Our city is very spread out."},{"time":416706,"text":"We have a great intersection of highways,"},{"time":420261,"text":"I mean, literally no traffic congestion\nin Oklahoma City to speak of."},{"time":423875,"text":"And so people live far, far away."},{"time":426086,"text":"Our city limits are enormous, 620 square miles,"},{"time":429671,"text":"but 15 miles is less than 15 minutes."},{"time":433216,"text":"You literally can get a speeding ticket"},{"time":435151,"text":"during rush hour in Oklahoma City."},{"time":438748,"text":"And as a result, people tend to spread out."},{"time":441245,"text":"Land's cheap."},{"time":444938,"text":"We had also not required developers"},{"time":447504,"text":"to build sidewalks on new developments \nfor a long, long time."},{"time":449999,"text":"We had fixed that, but it had been relatively recently,"},{"time":452412,"text":"and there were literally 100,000"},{"time":454806,"text":"or more homes into our inventory"},{"time":457482,"text":"in neighborhoods that had \nvirtually no level of walkability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465864,"text":"And as I tried to examine"},{"time":468118,"text":"how we might deal with obesity,"},{"time":470091,"text":"and was taking all of these elements into my mind,"},{"time":471975,"text":"I decided that the first thing we need to do"},{"time":475389,"text":"was have a conversation."},{"time":477509,"text":"You see, in Oklahoma City,"},{"time":479468,"text":"we weren't talking about obesity."},{"time":482249,"text":"And so, on New Year's Eve of 2007,"},{"time":487260,"text":"I went to the zoo,"},{"time":489299,"text":"and I stood in front of the elephants,"},{"time":491720,"text":"and I said, \"This city is going on a diet,"},{"time":495583,"text":"and we're going to lose a million pounds.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":499202,"text":"Well, that's when all hell broke loose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500975,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":503753,"text":"The national media"},{"time":505636,"text":"gravitated toward this story immediately,"},{"time":510153,"text":"and they really could have \ngone with it one of two ways."},{"time":513012,"text":"They could have said,"},{"time":514543,"text":"\"This city is so fat"},{"time":516685,"text":"that the mayor had to put them on a diet.\""},{"time":520001,"text":"But fortunately, the consensus was,"},{"time":522504,"text":"\"Look, this is a problem in a lot of places."},{"time":524851,"text":"This is a city that's wanting\nto do something about it.\""},{"time":528710,"text":"And so they started helping us"},{"time":530680,"text":"drive traffic to the website."},{"time":532830,"text":"Now, the web address was"},{"time":534348,"text":"thiscityisgoingonadiet.com."},{"time":539329,"text":"And I appeared on \"The Ellen DeGeneres Show\""},{"time":542748,"text":"one weekday morning to talk about the initiative,"},{"time":546168,"text":"and on that day, 150,000 visits"},{"time":549688,"text":"were placed to our website."},{"time":551508,"text":"People were signing up,"},{"time":553082,"text":"and so the pounds started to add up,"},{"time":555928,"text":"and the conversation that I thought"},{"time":557535,"text":"was so important to have was starting to take place."},{"time":561299,"text":"It was taking place inside the homes,"},{"time":563848,"text":"mothers and fathers talking about it with their kids."},{"time":566425,"text":"It was taking place in churches."},{"time":569086,"text":"Churches were starting their own running groups"},{"time":571082,"text":"and their own support groups"},{"time":572370,"text":"for people who were dealing with obesity."},{"time":575102,"text":"Suddenly, it was a topic worth discussing at schools"},{"time":578514,"text":"and in the workplace."},{"time":580146,"text":"And the large companies, they typically have"},{"time":582307,"text":"wonderful wellness programs,"},{"time":583903,"text":"but the medium-sized companies"},{"time":585226,"text":"that typically fall between the cracks\non issues like this,"},{"time":588311,"text":"they started to get engaged and used our program"},{"time":591012,"text":"as a model for their own employees"},{"time":592868,"text":"to try and have contests to see"},{"time":594814,"text":"who might be able to deal with their obesity situation"},{"time":598629,"text":"in a way that could be proactively\nbeneficial to others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603596,"text":"And then came the next stage of the equation."},{"time":608217,"text":"It was time to push what I called MAPS 3."},{"time":612229,"text":"Now MAPS 3, like the other two programs,"},{"time":614429,"text":"had had an economic development motive behind it,"},{"time":617093,"text":"but along with the traditional\neconomic development tasks"},{"time":619913,"text":"like building a new convention center,"},{"time":621675,"text":"we added some health-related infrastructure"},{"time":624439,"text":"to the process."},{"time":626331,"text":"We added a new central park, 70 acres in size,"},{"time":629076,"text":"to be right downtown in Oklahoma City."},{"time":631466,"text":"We're building a downtown streetcar"},{"time":633245,"text":"to try and help the walkability formula"},{"time":635493,"text":"for people who choose to live in the inner city"},{"time":637545,"text":"and help us create the density there."},{"time":640922,"text":"We're building senior health and wellness centers"},{"time":644277,"text":"throughout the community."},{"time":645975,"text":"We put some investments on the river"},{"time":647663,"text":"that had originally been invested upon"},{"time":650199,"text":"in the original MAPS,"},{"time":651879,"text":"and now we are currently in the final stages"},{"time":653823,"text":"of developing the finest venue in the world"},{"time":656474,"text":"for the sports of canoe, kayak and rowing."},{"time":659290,"text":"We hosted the Olympic trials last spring."},{"time":661182,"text":"We have Olympic-caliber events\ncoming to Oklahoma City,"},{"time":663586,"text":"and athletes from all over the world moving in,"},{"time":666142,"text":"along with inner city programs"},{"time":667744,"text":"to get kids more engaged in these\ntypes of recreational activities"},{"time":671694,"text":"that are a little bit nontraditional."},{"time":674494,"text":"We also, with another initiative that was passed,"},{"time":678220,"text":"are building hundreds of miles of new sidewalks"},{"time":682063,"text":"throughout the metro area."},{"time":684462,"text":"We're even going back into some"},{"time":686307,"text":"inner city situations"},{"time":687802,"text":"where we had built neighborhoods"},{"time":689516,"text":"and we had built schools"},{"time":691197,"text":"but we had not connected the two."},{"time":693123,"text":"We had built libraries and\nwe had built neighborhoods,"},{"time":695841,"text":"but we had never really connected the two"},{"time":697446,"text":"with any sort of walkability."},{"time":699870,"text":"Through yet another funding source,"},{"time":701969,"text":"we're redesigning all of our inner city streets"},{"time":705304,"text":"to be more pedestrian-friendly."},{"time":706814,"text":"Our streets were really wide,"},{"time":708691,"text":"and you'd push the button\nto allow you to walk across,"},{"time":711118,"text":"and you had to run in order to get there in time."},{"time":714666,"text":"But now we've narrowed the streets,"},{"time":716574,"text":"highly landscaped them, making them\nmore pedestrian-friendly,"},{"time":719482,"text":"really a redesign, rethinking the way"},{"time":721949,"text":"we build our infrastructure,"},{"time":723497,"text":"designing a city around people and not cars."},{"time":728744,"text":"We're completing our bicycle trail master plan."},{"time":730865,"text":"We'll have over 100 miles"},{"time":732683,"text":"when we're through building it out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":735475,"text":"And so you see this culture starting to shift"},{"time":738736,"text":"in Oklahoma City."},{"time":740240,"text":"And lo and behold, the demographic changes"},{"time":742917,"text":"that are coming with it are very inspiring."},{"time":745897,"text":"Highly educated twentysomethings"},{"time":747480,"text":"are moving to Oklahoma City from all over the region"},{"time":749540,"text":"and, indeed, even from further away, in California."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756715,"text":"When we reached a million pounds,"},{"time":759051,"text":"in January of 2012,"},{"time":761352,"text":"I flew to New York with some our participants"},{"time":763795,"text":"who had lost over 100 pounds,"},{"time":765325,"text":"whose lives had been changed,"},{"time":767610,"text":"and we appeared on the Rachael Ray show,"},{"time":769781,"text":"and then that afternoon,\nI did a round of media in New York"},{"time":773188,"text":"pushing the same messages"},{"time":775629,"text":"that you're accustomed to hearing\nabout obesity and the dangers of it."},{"time":779725,"text":"And I went into the lobby of Men's Fitness magazine,"},{"time":784706,"text":"the same magazine that had put us on that list"},{"time":789082,"text":"five years before."},{"time":791445,"text":"And as I'm sitting in the lobby\nwaiting to talk to the reporter,"},{"time":794402,"text":"I notice there's a magazine copy"},{"time":796786,"text":"of the current issue right there on the table,"},{"time":799405,"text":"and I pick it up, and I look at the headline"},{"time":801061,"text":"across the top, and it says,"},{"time":802826,"text":"\"America's Fattest Cities: Do You Live in One?\""},{"time":807507,"text":"Well, I knew I did,"},{"time":809652,"text":"so I picked up the magazine"},{"time":811804,"text":"and I began to look,"},{"time":814815,"text":"and we weren't on it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817561,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":823984,"text":"Then I looked on the list of fittest cities,"},{"time":826909,"text":"and we were on that list."},{"time":829072,"text":"We were on the list as the 22nd\nfittest city in the United States."},{"time":832450,"text":"Our state health statistics are doing better."},{"time":835637,"text":"Granted, we have a long way to go."},{"time":837749,"text":"Health is still not something"},{"time":838888,"text":"that we should be proud of in Oklahoma City,"},{"time":840425,"text":"but we seem to have turned the cultural shift"},{"time":844208,"text":"of making health a greater priority."},{"time":847289,"text":"And we love the idea of the demographics"},{"time":850132,"text":"of highly educated twentysomethings,"},{"time":851942,"text":"people with choices, choosing Oklahoma City"},{"time":853711,"text":"in large numbers."},{"time":855160,"text":"We have the lowest unemployment\nin the United States,"},{"time":857453,"text":"probably the strongest economy in the United States."},{"time":860325,"text":"And if you're like me, at some point"},{"time":861955,"text":"in your educational career,"},{"time":864327,"text":"you were asked to read a book called"},{"time":866544,"text":"\"The Grapes of Wrath.\""},{"time":869389,"text":"Oklahomans leaving for California"},{"time":872423,"text":"in large numbers for a better future."},{"time":874866,"text":"When we look at the demographic shifts"},{"time":876655,"text":"of people coming from the west,"},{"time":877815,"text":"it appears that what we're seeing now"},{"time":879443,"text":"is the wrath of grapes."},{"time":882291,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":884104,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":887169,"text":"The grandchildren are coming home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":891714,"text":"You've been a great audience and very attentive."},{"time":893502,"text":"Thank you very much for having me here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":895953,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}